# Chi Terminal — Product Specification
# Version 0.1.0 | March 2026

> The product contract. What we build, why, for whom, and how we know
> it's done. No code. No architecture. No implementation.

---

## Table of Contents

1. [Product Vision](#1-product-vision)
2. [Design Pillars](#2-design-pillars)
3. [Target Users](#3-target-users)
4. [Platform Targets](#4-platform-targets)
5. [Tier 1 — Core Terminal (MVP)](#5-tier-1--core-terminal-mvp)
6. [Tier 2 — Power Features](#6-tier-2--power-features)
7. [Tier 3 — Advanced & AI](#7-tier-3--advanced--ai)
