## 14. Build System

### 14.1 CMake Structure
CMakeLists.txt (root) ├── src/CMakeLists.txt │ ├── terminal/CMakeLists.txt → libchiterm-core (static) │ ├── rendering/CMakeLists.txt → libchiterm-render (static) │ ├── session/CMakeLists.txt → libchiterm-session (static) │ ├── config/CMakeLists.txt → libchiterm-config (static) │ ├── context/CMakeLists.txt → libchiterm-context (static) │ ├── platform/CMakeLists.txt → libchiterm-platform (static) │ ├── ai/CMakeLists.txt → libchiterm-ai (static, optional) │ └── app/CMakeLists.txt → chiterm (executable) ├── qml/CMakeLists.txt → QML module ├── tests/CMakeLists.txt → test executables └── third_party/CMakeLists.txt → external deps

text


Each module builds as a static library with explicit public headers.
The final executable links everything.

